	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 1 Ally (60 ft.) - 1 Minute - Magical</p><p>Using this ability consumes a use of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.HPrjgPXLsDRBbfsD]{Mark for Death}. You cannot use this ability alongside Mark for Death or any other ranger mark.</p><p><strong>Buff</strong> </p><ul><li><p>You surround your target with magical thorns. Whenever your target is struck by a melee attack, their attacker takes [[/r 1d4 magical piercing]] damage*. This ability ends early if you become &amp;reference[incapacitated].</p></li></ul><p><strong>Note: You'll need to manually deal damage using Mark of Thorns using the ranger who created it.</strong> </p><p></p><p>*This extra damage increases as you gain ranger levels. The damage dealt by this ability is equal to your Mark for Death damage.</p>",
